Subject: [PATCH 024/151] FogBugz #458420-2: ARM: dts: add lcd character panel

commit  1fbc0c26544af3233e7ef21a883f4eae0f0b8c09 from
https://github.com/altera-opensource/linux-socfpga.git
branch is socfpga-5.4.64-lts

Add Newhaven 2x16 character lcd panel for cyclone5, arria5, and
arria10 socdk.

Signed-off-by: Alan Tull <atull@kernel.org>
Signed-off-by: Meng Li <Meng.Li@windriver.com>
Integrated-by: Jun Zhang <jun.zhang@windriver.com>
---
